{
  "text": "Bosch-Banyeras et al. [CITATION_1] Left-sided Poland's syndrome, dextrocardia and Moebius syndrome [CITATION_2] Gugliantini et al. [CITATION_3] Left-sided Poland's syndrome, dextrocardia, diaphragmatic defect, aplasia of subtotal sternal body and hypoplasia of scapula, humerus, forearm bones 8",
